            "value" : "请为所选 Python 解释器安装 pymobiledevice3，以继续进行真机位置模拟。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install pymobiledevice3 into the same Python interpreter used by the device helper." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请将 pymobiledevice3 安装到设备辅助程序所使用的同一个 Python 解释器中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Python 3 on this Mac so `python3` resolves from your shell." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请在这台 Mac 上安装 Python 3，以便 shell 可以解析到 `python3`。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Install Xcode and open it once so Apple's developer tools finish setup and `xcrun` can access device and simulator tooling." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "请安装 Xcode 并启动一次，以便 Apple 的开发者工具完成设置，并让 `xcrun` 可以访问真机和模拟器工具。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
